{"tid":1238948,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[輕鬆一人一email] 投訴中文濫權教學助理劉文斌第二波攻勢正式展開","createTime":"2019-06-18T04:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T10:28:40.000Z","uid":43983,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f61aeb18a53a67961a53cf93811fdfb0fdf4fca8","tid":1238948,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:02:35.000Z","msg":"由於而家中文大學表明會暫停呢條仆街支那TA既職務，但佢依然可以享受緊政府，無錯，係我地既血汗錢提供比佢既每月17K studentship<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一日中大唔炒佢，大家一日都仲係輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地一齊用以下template send 投訴信</span></span>(多謝有巴打提供postgraduate handbook )去:<br />\ncusu@cuhk.edu.hk <span style=\"color: orange;\">(香港中文大學學生會)</span><br />\ngradschool@cuhk.edu.hk <span style=\"color: violet;\">(中文研究院)</span><br />\nwolff@cuhk.edu.hk <span style=\"color: green;\">(研究院院長)</span><br />\nhistory@cuhk.edu.hk <span style=\"color: navy;\">(中文歷史系)</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n敬啟者︰<br />\n<br />\n本人對貴校歷史系教學助理劉文斌因近日以學科評分恐嚇學生的濫權行為極度不滿，故特函投訴。<br />\n<br />\n根據貴校postgraduate handbook - Disciplinary Action 16.1章:<br />\n(e) an offence in connection with tests or examinations, or violation of any of the regulations governing conduct at tests or examinations as approved by the University from time to time;<br />\n(h) any conduct which is detrimental to the reputation and well‑being of the University;<br />\n劉曾於個人社交平台表示︰「你們這些本科生儘管去中環，去灣仔鬧，去罵內地人，下學期也不要哭著喊著求我給你考試通過」。他表明會以政治取向去評定學生成績，並對貴校校譽造成嚴重損害，明顯違反以上(e),(h)兩項守則。<br />\n<br />\n雖然貴校已暫不安排劉在來年續任助教，但其研究生身份仍每個月受政府資助，就應當受到大眾的監察，作為普眾大眾的一員，我仍對劉濫用職權感到極到遺憾和憤怒！更認為此等研究生嚴重損害貴校之校譽。本人現強烈要求貴校對該濫權的研究生作出嚴厲處分或終止學位，並再次就劉的去留向公眾作出交代。<br />\n<br />\n一位憤怒的香港市民<br />\nXXX上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">對抗支那劣質文化，匹夫有責，我地而家一人一email 推撚到中大處分件濫權仆街為止</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\np.s.歡迎各路巴打完善下個template<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d163835247599da2c893ab406cd58d6c664c58","tid":1238948,"uid":43983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:04:46.000Z","msg":"漏左個email subject<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投訴歷史系教學助理劉文斌 恐嚇學生 濫用職權</span></span>"},{"pid":"28aa01dd525fd2120118f31258c8728e018f66ee","tid":1238948,"uid":112613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:05:49.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"5306a1e62e89a7408ecea56280c79821eb21abf2","tid":1238948,"uid":166616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n無連登仔理?  守護年青人"},{"pid":"f94efa98d09d015e064bd3e4119cdf44f3294a5a","tid":1238948,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:08:31.000Z","msg":"自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45cf33974cc4177ab197723f2f092e1122355df5","tid":1238948,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad73ae0e7cd46f97e9762c7f9581254d50